7389 - Business Services, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > INDEED AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover business services, not elsewhere classified. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. INDEED AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by head of sales & director Takashi Nishimura. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $31.08 million. Its net profit totalled $429,000. INDEED AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the services industry sector.
